          "report": "REFLECT STAGE: Strategy analysis of all 22 issues.\n\nThree root causes drive the genuine issues:\n\n1. ERROR VISIBILITY (2 genuine): [review::.::holistic::error_consistency::broad_catch_no_discrimination] and [review::.::holistic::error_consistency::silent_error_swallowing] share the same root: fetchGitHub swallows all errors silently. Fix: add console.warn for non-ok responses (with status) and caught exceptions (with error message).\n\n2. TEST COVERAGE GAPS (2 genuine): [review::.::holistic::test_strategy::untested_fetch_functions] and [review::.::holistic::test_strategy::untested_server_load] share the root: only pure functions are tested. Fix: add vitest tests with vi.fn() mocking global fetch.\n\n3. TYPE PRECISION (3 genuine): [review::.::holistic::type_safety::fetchJson_untyped_return], [review::.::holistic::type_safety::unused_interface_field], and [review::.::holistic::naming_quality::fetchJson_hides_null] cluster around fetchJson. Fix: rename to tryFetchJson, change return type to Promise<unknown | null>, remove language from RepoResponse.\n\n4. CONVENTION CONSISTENCY (1 genuine): [review::.::holistic::convention_outlier::mixed_lifecycle_pattern] Terminal.svelte uses onMount instead of $effect. Simple migration.\n\n5. LOW-PRIORITY ARCHITECTURE (3 genuine): [review::.::holistic::cross_module_architecture::parallel_project_imports], [review::.::holistic::mid_level_elegance::github_data_merge_in_presentation], and [review::.::holistic::api_surface_coherence::internal_helpers_exported_for_testing] are valid but low-impact.\n\n6. CONTENT (1 genuine): [review::.::holistic::ai_generated_debt::uniform_description_prose] is a content decision.\n\n7. ALREADY FIXED - FALSE POSITIVES (7 issues):\n[review::.::holistic::abstraction_fitness::runtime_value_in_types_module] - accentColors moved to constants.ts\n[review::.::holistic::high_level_elegance::runtime_value_in_types_module] - same fix\n[review::.::holistic::package_organization::types_dir_mix